| `.replit` | Replit run/deploy config | Delete entirely |
| `.replitignore` | Replit-specific ignore | Delete entirely |
| `.npmrc` | May contain Replit registry | Review/replace |
| `pnpm-workspace.yaml` | `@replit/*` package exclusions, linux-x64-only overrides | Rewrite completely |
| `vite.config.ts` | `@replit/vite-plugin-runtime-error-modal`, `@replit/vite-plugin-cartographer`, `@replit/vite-plugin-dev-banner`, `REPL_ID` checks | Remove all 3 plugins |
| `package.json` (global-college) | `@replit/vite-plugin-*` (3 packages) in devDependencies | Remove |
| `vite.config.ts` | `PORT` and `BASE_PATH` env vars required at build time | Make optional with defaults |
| `api-server/index.ts` | Hardcoded PORT requirement | Add default port fallback |
| `.agents/` directory | Replit AI agent config | Delete entirely |
| `.local/` directory | Replit local state | Delete entirely |
| `replit.md` | Replit project docs | Delete |

