## 4. What Has Been Done ✅

### 4.1 Database Schemas (Drizzle ORM) — Partially Done
17 schema files exist with basic table definitions:

| Table | Fields | Status |
|-------|--------|--------|
| `users` | id, name, email, passwordHash, role, phone, cnic, avatar, isActive | ⚠️ Missing: branchId, isEmailVerified, isIdentityVerified, lockedUntil, failedLoginAttempts |
| `courses` | id, title, description, category, duration, fee, thumbnail, syllabus, teacherId, isFeatured, isFree | ⚠️ Missing: slug, status (DRAFT/PENDING/LIVE/ARCHIVED), rejectionNote, totalDurationHours |
| `lessons` | id, courseId, title, description, videoUrl, pdfUrl, duration, orderIndex | ⚠️ Missing: sectionId (no Section model!), encryptedYoutubeId, completionThreshold |
| `enrollments` | id, userId, courseId, progress, status | ⚠️ Missing: completedAt, isCompleted |
| `payments` | id, userId, courseId, amount, method, status, receiptUrl, notes | ⚠️ Missing: rejectionReason, reviewedAt, reviewedBy |
| `quizzes` | id, courseId, title, questions(jsonb), totalMarks, timeLimit | ⚠️ Missing: lessonId, passingScore. Questions are JSON blob instead of separate table |
| `assignments` | id, courseId, title, description, dueDate, totalMarks | ⚠️ Missing: lessonId, instructions, allowLateSubmission |
| `certificates` | id, userId, courseId, certificateNumber | ⚠️ Missing: pdfUrl, status, isRevoked, issuedAt |
| `branches` | id, name, city, address, phone, email, mapUrl, isMain | ✅ Adequate |
| `settings` | id, key, value, label, category | ✅ Adequate |
| `notifications` | Basic structure exists | ⚠️ Missing: link field |
| `forum` | forumPosts + forumReplies tables | ⚠️ Missing: upvotes, isPinned |
| `messages` | messageThreads + messages tables | ⚠️ Simplified |
| `identity-verification` | Basic structure | ⚠️ Missing: rejectionReason |
| `testimonials` | Basic structure | ✅ Adequate |
| `success-stories` | Basic structure | ✅ Adequate |

**Critical Missing Tables:**
- ❌ `Section` model (courses have no sections/chapters)
- ❌ `LessonCompletion` (only simplified `lessonProgress`)
- ❌ `VideoAccessLog`
- ❌ `Question` (questions stored as JSON in quizzes)
- ❌ `QuizAttempt` (only `quizResults`)

### 4.2 Backend API (Express.js) — Shell Only
21 route files exist but most contain **basic CRUD with no business logic**:

| Route File | Endpoints | Functional? |
|-----------|-----------|-------------|
| `auth.ts` | login, register, logout, /auth/me | ⚠️ Works but uses in-memory sessions, SHA-256 (not bcrypt) |
| `courses.ts` | GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /courses | ⚠️ Basic CRUD, no role checks |
| `branches.ts` | CRUD for branches | ⚠️ Basic CRUD, no admin guard |
| `lessons.ts` | CRUD for lessons | ⚠️ Basic CRUD |
| `enrollments.ts` | Basic enrollment | ⚠️ No payment flow integration |
| `payments.ts` | Basic payment CRUD | ⚠️ No approve/reject flow |
| `dashboard.ts` | Admin/Student/Teacher stats | ⚠️ Returns aggregated data |
| Other 14 files | Various routes | ⚠️ Minimal implementation |

**Critical Backend Gaps:**
- ❌ **No JWT authentication** — uses volatile in-memory `Map<string, session>`
- ❌ **No bcrypt** — uses SHA-256 for password hashing (insecure)
- ❌ **No middleware** — `middlewares/` folder contains only `.gitkeep`
- ❌ **No RBAC** — any user can access any endpoint
- ❌ **No file upload** — no Cloudinary/multer integration
- ❌ **No email service** — no Nodemailer/SendGrid
- ❌ **No video protection** — no AES encryption, no stream tokens
- ❌ **No error handling** — no AppError class, no global error handler
- ❌ **No input validation middleware** — Zod schemas exist but not enforced
- ❌ **No API versioning** — routes at `/api/` not `/api/v1/`
- ❌ **No rate limiting** — no express-rate-limit
- ❌ **No security headers** — no helmet
- ❌ **No pagination** — all queries return full datasets
- ❌ **No transaction support** — no Drizzle transactions used

