## 8. What Must Be Done — Development Roadmap

### Phase 1: Foundation & Independence (Week 1)
1. **Remove ALL Replit dependencies** — clean folder structure
2. **Restructure to standard monorepo**: `/client` + `/server` + `/prisma` OR keep Drizzle with proper `/db`
3. **Implement proper JWT authentication** with bcrypt, access/refresh tokens
4. **Build RBAC middleware** — `authenticate()` + `authorize(roles)`
5. **Add global error handling** — AppError class + error middleware
6. **Fix database schema** — add all missing fields, Section model, proper relationships
7. **Run and verify migrations** against real PostgreSQL
8. **Add `.env.example`** with all required environment variables
9. **Add API versioning** — `/api/v1/` prefix

### Phase 2: Core LMS Engine (Weeks 2-3)
10. **Course + Section + Lesson CRUD** with proper structure
11. **YouTube video protection system** — AES-256 encryption, stream tokens, sandboxed iframe
12. **Video completion tracking** — 5-second interval, fraud prevention
13. **Enrollment system** — free (immediate) + paid (pending payment)
14. **Payment flow** — submit receipt → admin review → approve/reject → auto-enroll
15. **File upload service** — Cloudinary integration for PDFs, receipts, images

### Phase 3: Assessment & Certification (Weeks 3-4)
16. **Quiz system** — builder, taker, auto-grading, results
17. **Assignment system** — create, submit, grade, feedback
18. **Certificate system** — completion check, PDF generation, verification
19. **Identity verification** — CNIC/Form-B upload, admin review, cert unlock

### Phase 4: Communication (Week 4)
20. **Messaging system** — student↔teacher threads
21. **Discussion forum** — per-course posts, replies, pinning, upvotes
22. **Email service** — Nodemailer + templates for all events
23. **Notification system** — all triggers implemented
24. **Announcement system** — admin → targeted groups

### Phase 5: Admin Power Features (Week 5)
25. **Admin dashboard** — comprehensive KPIs, pending action trays
26. **Student/Teacher management** — full detail views, edit, disable, password reset
27. **Course review/approval workflow**
28. **Reports** — branch, enrollment, revenue, student progress with PDF/Excel export
29. **Admin settings** — payment details, certificate config, site settings, email templates
30. **Content management** — success stories, testimonials with drag reorder

### Phase 6: Frontend Polish (Week 6)
31. **Rebuild public website** — all 12 pages with full sections as per PRD
32. **Student portal** — all 14 pages, especially the video learning page
33. **Teacher panel** — all 9 pages, especially course builder and grading
34. **Admin panel** — all 18 pages with full functionality
35. **Mobile responsiveness** — all pages
36. **WhatsApp floating button**, social media links, Google Maps

### Phase 7: Production Readiness (Week 7)
37. **Security hardening** — helmet, rate limiting, CORS, input sanitization
38. **Performance optimization** — pagination, caching, lazy loading
39. **Testing** — end-to-end critical flows
40. **Deployment configuration** — Docker, env validation, health checks
41. **README.md** with setup, deployment, and API documentation

